* Iron Raptor arrived at the scene and saw Liono begin to fight Megatron, 
she looked over at Plintissa and smiled.*

" Told you I'd be here. Now, do as your commander says and get your 
skid-plate back to base."

* Looks at the 3 Predacons and sighs,never a dull day was there?*

" Iron Raptor, Maximize!!"

* Now transformed she glared at Megatron and snarled, it was strange yet 
topical at how the Preds always ganged up on lone bots! She took out her 
splatter gun and aimed it Sensis's head, a perfect target!
Iron Raptor pulled the trigger...*
